<h4><br>Why is homemade food trending?<br></h4>
<ul id="benefits-info">
    <li><span class="bold"style="margin:0;">Nutritional value in view of the fact that they tend to be more nutritious.  </span></li>
    <li><span class="bold">Cost effective seeing that its more friendly than dining out.</span>
    <li><span class="bold">Family bonding because cooking and eating together as a family can strengthen relationships and creat meaningful memories. </span></li>
    <li><span class="bold">Learning experience given that cooking at home provides an opportunity to earn new recipes,culinary techniques and improve cooking skills</span></li>
</ul>
